   PL/SQL trigger automation
   Business intelligence query design
   KPI development and reporting logic
   Scalable dataset generation

Real-World Application:
   This system reflects core components of production environments used in:
      Gym membership systems
      Subscription-based SaaS platforms
      Customer lifecycle management systems
      Operational reporting dashboards

